                "invention-title": [
                    "Magnesium-hydrogen co-production method with negative carbon emission",
                    "负碳排放的镁氢联产方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a negative carbon emission magnesium-hydrogen co-production method which comprises the following steps: S00, preparing magnesium oxide by using seawater or salt lake brine, and carrying out medium-temperature pyrolysis on biomass wastes to obtain biological carbon particles; s10, adopting green electricity, carrying out carbon thermal reduction on magnesium oxide and the biochar particles in an electric arc furnace to smelt magnesium, carrying out quenching condensation to obtain magnesium metal, and transforming the byproduct carbon monoxide and water vapor to obtain carbon dioxide and hydrogen; and S20, carbon dioxide and hydrogen are separated, carbon dioxide is subjected to carbon capture and storage, and hydrogen and magnesium metal are synthesized to generate magnesium hydride and stored. According to the method, high-concentration and high-purity CO2 gas obtained after conversion of the byproduct CO in carbothermic magnesium smelting is easily subjected to low-cost CCUS, negative carbonization is achieved, the byproduct CO gas in the magnesium smelting process can be directly converted into equivalent hydrogen, the hydrogen and the main product magnesium metal are suitable for being combined into a stable and safe solid hydrogen storage magnesium alloy, and the method is suitable for long-distance low-cost transportation."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及负碳排放的镁氢联产方法，该方案包括以下步骤：S00、利用海水或盐湖卤水制备氧化镁，将生物质废弃物进行中温热解，以获得生物碳粒子；S10、采用绿电，在电弧炉中将氧化镁和生物碳粒子进行碳热还原炼镁，并进行淬冷冷凝获得金属镁，副产得到的一氧化碳与水蒸气变换得到二氧化碳和氢气；S20、分离二氧化碳和氢气，将二氧化碳进行碳捕集封存，将氢气与金属镁合成生成二氢化镁并存储。本发明在碳热炼镁副产CO变换后得到的高浓度、高纯度CO2气体，容易进行低成本CCUS，实现负碳化，还能够在炼镁过程副产的CO气体直接转变为等量氢气，氢气与主产品金属镁适合结合成稳定、安全的固体储氢镁合金，适合长距离低成本运输。"
                }
            ]
